 Arizona Beverage Company Logo
Arizona Beverages USA is an American producer of many flavors of iced tea, juice cocktails, and energy drinks based in Woodbury, New York. Arizona’s first product was made available in 1992. Arizona is known for its “Big Can” drinks holding 23 fl. oz. of iced teas, juice drinks and other beverages that retail for around the price of US$0.99 in the United States and C$1.29 in Canada. In certain stores, patrons may find a smaller Arizona Tea Can for the price of only US$0.
